{"lastModified":1761300602497,"uri":"c::8183534776::vessel::22eb8090-f0ff-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: South of France, Corsica, Sardinia, Italy, Balearics\n \nNEOW is an exceptional Alegria 67 by Fountaine Pajot, where sophisticated craftsmanship blends seamlessly with superior comfort and sailing performance. Designed for those who crave elegance at sea, this premier catamaran offers generous outdoor areas, refined interiors, and a smart, spacious layout perfect for both peaceful cruising and entertaining guests.\n\n• She accommodates 8 guests into 4 luxurious double cabins, including a full-beam Master suite with a dedicated team of 3 professionals at your service\n\nHighlights Onboard:\n• Expansive flybridge with lounge area, sunbeds, and a fully equipped wet bar\n• Optional Jacuzzi and lounge space on the foredeck\n• Stylish saloon filled with natural light and sweeping ocean views\n• Fully appointed galley with indoor and outdoor dining areas\n• Smooth and stable sailing, combining power with comfort\n• Selection of water toys and onboard activities for all ages\n\nNEOW offers more than just a sailing holiday—it’s a tailored yachting experience. The attentive crew ensures every aspect of your charter is thoughtfully arranged, from curated meals to customized itineraries.\n\nWhether you’re seeking a peaceful getaway or a vibrant group adventure, NEOW is your private sanctuary at sea.\n","blueprint":{"name":"NEOW","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::22eb8090-f0ff-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::42a10910-3fd1-11f0-a77c-b921fb280ccd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22eb8090-f0ff-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::429ac780-3fd1-11f0-a77c-b921fb280ccd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22eb8090-f0ff-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::429b3cb0-3fd1-11f0-a77c-b921fb280ccd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::22eb8090-f0ff-11ee-846a-95451e44ba13::assets::4298